            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CueNow 1.0.3

- Fixed Sparkle update package signing so in-app updates install cleanly.
- Added release packaging verification for the app inside the DMG and nested Sparkle helpers.
- Fixed pre-update note saving so current notes and archived notes are flushed before backups are created.
]]></description>
